metadata.name: Kentucky Fried Crickets
metadata.description:
Step right up folks, the World Economic Forum has a new KFC, but this ain't your grandma's fried chicken joint! This one stands for Kentucky Fried Crickets and it's going to rock your taste buds. After the bird flu scare, we figured why not go for the gold and enjoy some crispy, crunchy and delicious insects. And the best part? By 2030, you won't even own anything and still be as happy as a cricket on a hot summer day! So come on in and give KFC a try, your taste buds will thank you!

Image was created by prompting OpenAi's Dall-E-2 and the short description was brought to life with the help of ChatGPT-3. Postprocessing was done with Procreate.
